## Development Status :open_book:

The current version of the Extension through which applications will be launched is available in the Google Web Store - https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/mutable-web/cnahdmdbhkphpbpbjjbfdnmbphbenglc

We also launched a fork of Near.Social supporting community versions (Mutations), in which the applications we are going to develop will also be available. - https://social.dapplets.org/

After we shifted to using NEAR B.O.S in our solution we attended 4 hackathons to get some approval for this new conception. All entries were successful and we won first prizes in all the tracks we participated in.

