### Overview

- **Total Estimated Duration:** 3 months
- **Full-Time Equivalent (FTE):**  2 FTE
- **Total Costs:** 18,000 USD


### Milestone 1 — NFT Saler

- **Estimated duration:** 1 month
- **FTE:**  2
- **Costs:** 6,000 USD

| Number | Deliverable | Specification |
| -----: | ----------- | ------------- |
| 0a. | License | Apache 2.0 / GPLv3 / MIT / Unlicense |
| 0b. | Documentation | Documentation of the code and a tutorial that explains how a developer can build and deploy a similar application and submit it to Mutation. |
| 0c. | Testing Guide | Core functions will be fully covered by unit tests. There also will be a guide to run tests on your own |
| 0d. | Article | We will publish an article in Medium about the new opportunity to run such applications using our platform and Mintbase resources.) |
| 1. | NFT Saler Widget | BOS Application that can be injected to post on Twitter, Reddit, and LinkedIn. A user provides an Affiliate Direct link to insert NFT Offer to the page. Other users can use it to buy NFT. |  
| 2. | NFT Saler Dashboard | Web App in which each logged-in user can see the injections with NFT that he has posted within different resources, the number of their views, and whether there were sales. It can also be used to remove injections. |  


### Milestone 2 — NFT illustrator widget

- **Estimated duration:** 1 month
- **FTE:**  2
