| 1. | NFT illustrator widget | BOS Application that can be injected to post on Twitter, Reddit, and LinkedIn. The application takes the context of the post in which it is embedded, enriches the text with an additional prompt, and requests an AI image generation service. The resulting image is offered to be minted as an NFT illustration for the post. |  
| 2. | NFT illustrator Dashboard | Web App that gives access to a list of all user-generated illustrations. As well as a list of all user-generated illustrations with post titles to attract interest in the content. |  


